hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
7246,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. ham sab jawan aur ham umr they, ham aap ki khidmat mein bees din tak thahrey rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut shafeeq they. jab aap ne malum kya ke ab hamara dil apne ghar walon ki taraf mushtaaq hai to aap ne ham se puchha ke apne peechhey ham kin logon ko chhod kar aaey hain. ham ne aapko bataya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ghar chaley jao aur unke sath raho aur unhein Islam sikhaao aur Deen bataao aur bahut si baatein aap ne kahin jin mein kuchh mujhey yad nahi hain aur kuchh yad hain aur (farmaayaa ke) jis tarah mujhey tum ne Namaz padhtey dekha isi tarah Namaz padho. isliye jab Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to tum mein se aik tumharey liye azan kahey aur jo umr mein sabse bada ho wo imamat karaaey."
7247,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi shakhs ko Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki azan sehrii khaney se na rokey kyonke wo sirf isliye azan detey hain taake jo Namaz ke liye bedaar hain wo wapas aa jayen aur jo soey huey hain wo bedaar ho jayen aur fajr wo nahi hai jo is tarah lambi dhaar hoti hai. Yahya ne iske izhar ke liye apne donon hath milaaey aur kaha yahan tak ke wo is tarah zahir ho jaey aur uske izhar ke liye unhon-ne apni donon shahadat ki ungliyon ko phaila kar batlaayaa.''
7248,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Bilal ( Ramazan mein) raat hi mein azan detey hain (wo namaaze fajr ki azan nahi hotii) isliye tum khaao piyo, yahan tak ke Abdullaah-ibne-umme-Maktoom azan dein (to khana peenaa band kar do).''"
7249,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Zohar ki panch rakaat Namaz padhai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : kya Namaz (ki rak'aton) mein kuchh badh gaya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat hai? sahaba ne kaha ke aap ne panch rakaat Namaz padhai hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam ke baad do sajdey (saho ke) kiye.
7250,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do hi rakaat par (maghrib ya isha ki Namaz mein) Namaz khatm kar di to zul-yadain (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! Namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya zul-yadain sahi kehtey hain? logon ne kaha ji haan. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur aakhiri rakatein padhein phir salam pheraa, takbeer ki aur sajda kya (namaz ke aam) sajdey jaisa ya us se lambaa, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar uthaayaa, phir takbeer kahi aur Namaz ke sajdey jaisa sajda kya, phir sar uthaayaa."
7251,"masjide-Qubaa mein log subah ki Namaz padh rahe they ke aik aaney waley ne unke paas pahunch kar kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par raat Quran ki aayat nazil hui hai aur aapko hukm diya gaya hai ke Namaz mein Kaba ki taraf munh kar lein isliye tum bhi usi taraf rukh kar lo. un logon ke chehrey Sham (Syria) (yani baitul-maqdis) ki taraf they, phir wo log Kaba ki taraf mud gaey."
7252,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to aap sola ya satrah mahiney tak baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhtey rahe lekin aap ki aarzoo thi ke Kaba ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhein. phir Allah Taala ne (sura al-Baqara mein) ye aayat nazil ki (قد نرى تقلب وجهك في السماء فلنولينك قبلة ترضاها) ''ham aap ke munh ke baar-baar aasman ki taraf uthney ko dekhtey hain, an-qareeb ham aap ke munh ko is qible ki taraf pher dengey jis se aap khush hongey.'' chunanche rukh Kaba ki taraf kar diya gaya. aik sahib ne Asr ki Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi, phir wo Madina se nikal kar Ansar ki aik jamat tak pahunchey aur kaha ke wo gawahi detey hain ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi hai aur Kaba ki taraf munh karne ka hukm ho gaya hai chunanche sab log Kaba rukh ho gaey halanke wo Asr ki Namaz ke rukoo mein they."
7253,"mein abu-Talha Ansari , abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko khajoor ki sharab pilaa raha tha. itney mein aik aaney waley shakhs ne aa kar khabar di ke sharab haram kar di gaee hai. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne us shakhs ki khabar suntey hi kaha : Anas! un matkon ko badh kar sab ko tod de. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main aik haawan-dasta ki taraf badha jo hamarey paas tha aur maine iske nichley hissey se un matkon par maara jis se wo sab toot gaey."
7254,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahal Najran se farmaya ''main tumharey paas aik amanat daar aadmi jo haqiqi amanat daar hoga bhejoonga.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba muntazir rahe (ke kon us sifat se mausoof hai) to aap ne abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhejaa.
7255,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har ummat mein aik amanat daar hota hai aur is ummat ke amanat daar abu-Ubaida ibne-Jarraah (rz) hain.''
7256,qabila Ansar ke aik sahib they (aos bin khaulaa naam ( jab wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein shirkat na kar saktey aur main Sharik hota to unhein aa kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis ki khabrein bataataa aur jab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein Sharik na ho paata aur wo Sharik hotey to wo aa kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis ki khabar mujhey bataatey .
7257,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar bheja aur uska ameer aik sahib Abdullah-bin Huzafa Sehmi ko banaya, phir (is ne kya kya ke) aag jalwaaii aur) lashkariyon se) kaha ke usmein dakhil ho jao . jis par kuchh logon ne dakhil hona chaha lekin kuchh logon ne kaha ke ham aag hi se bhag kar aaey hain. phir iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke jinhoney aag mein dakhil honey ka irada kya tha ke agar tum usmein dakhil ho jatey to usmein qiyamat tak rahtey aur doosrey logon se kaha ke Allah Taala ki nafarmani mein kisi ki itaat halal nahi hai itaat sirf nek kaamon mein hai."
7258,2 log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas apna jhagdaa laey. dusri sanad aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha (tafseel aagey nichey ki hadis mein hai).
7259,2 log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas apna jhagdaa laey. dusri sanad aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha (tafseel aagey nichey ki hadis mein hai).
7260,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas maujood they ke dehaatiyon mein se aik sahib khadey huey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! kitabullah ke mutabiq mera faisla farma dijiye. iske baad unka muqabil fareeq khada hua aur kaha unhon-ne sahi kaha ya Rasulullah ! hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye aur mujhey kehney ki ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho. unhon-ne kaha ke mera ladka unke yahan mazdoorii kya karta tha, ( Aseef ( ba-maanaa ( الأجير ( mazdoor hai, phir us ne unki aurat se zina kar liya to logon ne mujhey bataya ke mere betey par rajm (sangsaar) ki saza hogi lekin maine uski taraf se so bakriyon aur aik baandi ka fidya diya (aur ladkey ko chhudaa liya ( phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke uski biwi par rajm (sangsaar) ki saza laagu hogi aur mere ladkey ko so kode aur aik saal ke liye jilaa watanii ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! main tumharey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla karunga, baandi aur bakriyan to usey wapas kar do aur tumharey ladkey par so kode aur aik saal jilaa watanii ki saza hai aur aey Anees! ( qabila Aslam ke aik sahabi ( uski biwi ke paas jao, agar wo zina ka iqrar karey to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do. chunanche Anees (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas gaey aur us ne iqrar kar liya phir Anees (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko sangsaar kar dala."
7261,"maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, bayan kya ke Khandaq ki jang ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dushman se khabar laney ke liye) sahaba se kaha to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) taiyaar ho gaey phir unse kaha to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) hi taiyaar huey. phir kaha, phir bhi unhon-ne hi aamaadagii dikhlai . iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har Nabi ke hawaarii ( madadgaar ( hotey hain aur mere hawaarii Zuber hain. aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya ke maine ye riwayat ibne-Munkadir se yad ki aur Ayub ne ibne-munkadir se kaha, aey abu-Bakar! (ye Muhammad-bin Munkadir ki kunniyat hai) unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan kijiye kyonke log pasand kartey hain ke aap Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadisein bayan karein to unhon-ne usi majlis mein kaha ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur char hadison mein pai-dar-pai ye kaha ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha ke maine Sufiyan-bin-Uena se kaha ke Sufiyan Sory to jang Qureza kehtey hain ( bajaey Khandaq ki jang ke) unhon-ne kaha ke maine itney hi yaqin ke sath yad kya hai jaisa ke tum us waqt baithey ho ke unhon-ne Khandaq ki jang kaha, Sufiyan ne kaha ke ye donon aik hi jang hain (kyonke) Khandaq ki jang ke fauran baad isi din jang Qureza pesh aaya aur wo muskuraaey ."
7262,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik baagh mein dakhil huey aur mujhey darwaze ki nigrani ka hukm diya, phir aik sahabi aaey aur ijazat chahi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat de do. wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat de do, phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bhi ijazat de do aur jannat ki bashaarat de do."
7263,mein hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne bula khaane mein tashrif rakhtey they aur aap ka aik kala ghulam seedhi ke uper ( nigrani kar raha ( tha maine us se kaha ke kaho ke umr bin-Khattab khada hai aur ijazat chahta hai.
7264,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kisraa parwez Shah Iraan ko khat bheja aur qaasid Abdullah-bin Huzafa (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke khat Bahrain ke governer munzir bin saawii ke hawale karein wo usey Kisraa tak pahunchaaeyga. jab Kisraa ne wo khat padha to usey phaad diya. mujhey yad hai ke Saeed bin Musaiyab ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey baddua di ke Allah unhein bhi tukdey tukdey kar de.
7265,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Aslam ke aik sahib Hind bin Asma se farmaya ke apni qaum mein ya logon mein elaan kar do aashoora ke din ke jisne kha liya ho wo apna Baqiiya din (be khaaey ( pura karey aur us ne na khaya ho wo roza rakhey .
7266,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey khas apne takht par bitha letey they. unhon-ne aik baar bayan kya ke qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad aaya jab wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kis qaum ka wafad hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Rabee qabila ka ( abdul-Qais usi qabeeley ki aik shaakh hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Mubarak ho us wafad ko ya yun farmaya ke Mubarak ho bila ruswai aur sharmindagi uthaney aaey ho. unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey aur aap ke beech mein Muzar kaafiron ka mulk padta hai. aap hamein aisi baat ka hukm dijiye jis se ham jannat mein dakhil hon aur peechhey reh janey walon ko bhi bataaein. phir unhon-ne sharab ke bartanon ke mutaalliq puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein char chizon se rokaa aur char chizon ka hukm diya. aap ne eman billah ka hukm diya. malum farmaya jantey ho eman billah kya cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Allah aur uska rasool zyada jantey hain. farmaya ke gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain aur Namaz qaaim karne ka ( hukm diyaa) aur zakat deney kaa. mera khayal hai ke hadis mein Ramazan ke rozon ka bhi zikr hai aur ghaneemat mein se panchwan hissey (baitul-maal) mein dena aur aap ne unhein dabbaa, hantam, muzaffat aur naqeer ke bartan (jin mein Arab log sharab rakhtey aur banatey they) ke istemal se mana kya aur kabhi-kabhi muqeer kaha, farmaya ke unhein yad rakho aur unhein pahuncha do jo nahi aa sakey hain."
7267,"tum ne dekha imam Hasan Basri Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kitni hadis ( mursalan ( riwayat kartey hain. main ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein taqriban dhaai saal raha lekin maine unko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is hadis ke siwa aur koi hadis bayan kartey nahi suna. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kai ashaab jin mein Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they ( dastar-khuwaan par baithey huey they) logon ne gosht khaney ke liye hath badhaya to paak beeviyon mein se aik paak bevi Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne aagah kya ke ye saandey ka gosht hai. sab log khaney se ruk gaey, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khaao (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( كلوا ( farmaya ya ( اطعموا ( isliye ke halal hai ya farmaya ke is khaney mein koi harj nahi albatta ye janwar meri khuraak nahi hai, mujh ko iske khaney se aik qism ki nafrat aati hai."
